# Summons item displays and edits items properly, end of potted plant raycast

data remove storage myriad:temp root
data modify storage myriad:temp root.item set from entity @s SelectedItem
data modify storage myriad:temp root.item.count set value 1
swing
item modify entity @s[gamemode=!creative] weapon.mainhand myriad:reduce_count

